{"tid":2400050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【林鄭視察佐敦文英樓  居民連叫三次「八婆，快啲去死！」】","createTime":"2021-02-08T15:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T17:02:57.000Z","uid":5195,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"47ed2fa70ecd2d0713a141cb6c3419a2f8bce86d","tid":2400050,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"【林鄭視察佐敦文英樓  居民連叫三次「八婆，快啲去死！」】<br />\n<br />\n政府晚上第九次突襲油尖旺，將佐敦渡船角文英街2-24號文英樓列為受限區域，居民須接受強制檢測。行政長官林鄭月娥晚上到場視察，期間有居民連續高呼三次「八婆，快啲去死」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在近9時40分乘坐一輛黑色七人車到達文匯街停車場，大批軍裝警員一早在場等候及清空馬路。林鄭甫下車即遭油尖旺區議會副主席余德寶開咪追擊：「你封咗油尖旺9次呀，你係咪好憎我哋油尖旺？」林鄭沒有回應，隨即聯同10多名工作人員一同巡視檢測情況，並多次與檢測人員交談。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭視察約10分鐘後離開臨時檢測站，沿渡船街轉到文英樓外視察，勉勵一眾穿著保護衣的人員。她臨走前向記者舉手點頭示意，但未有發言，在10時便乘車離開。<br />\n<br />\n #突襲封區<br />\n【文英樓列受限區域 運輸司機：一個癲婆害七百萬人】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/39ZdJCz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39ZdJCz&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=44c45c5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39ZdJCz</a><br />\n【陳梓維受限區內直播 籲居民可向自己求助 警嘲「傻仔區議員」】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3rDccIl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3rDccIl&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=db14ee0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3rDccIl</a><br />\n<br />\n支持獨媒：<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/supportus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fsupportus&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=2222d38f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fsupportus&h=7408529f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/supportus</a><br />\n <br />\n#社區新聞計劃 區區有區報：<br />\n<a href=\"http://collaction.hk/s/communitynews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcollaction.hk%2Fs%2Fcommunitynews&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=2e743677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">collaction.hk/s/communitynews</a>"},{"pi